{"tid":314792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（核武時代終結？）122國通過禁止核武","createTime":"2017-07-09T13:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T09:15:50.000Z","uid":22440,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"47ab937bb206f816f7b57f4cf6ca31646ef6327b","tid":314792,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"全球超過120個國家在聯合國會議上通過歷來首條具法律約束力的禁止核武條約，但所有擁有核武的國家都缺席會議。<br />\n<br />\n負責主持有關會議的主席哥斯達黎加大使高美斯(Elayne Whyte Gomez)在熱烈的歡呼聲下宣佈有122個國家贊成該項歷史性條約，荷蘭反對，而新加坡則投棄權票。她說，129個國家參與草擬條約，佔聯合國193個會員國的三分二，但所有擁有核武的國家和北約成員國都杯葛談判，只有荷蘭因國會敦促派代表團參與討論才列席其中。<br />\n目前已知或相信擁有核武的9個國家，包括美國、俄羅斯、英國、中國、法國、印度、巴基斯坦、北韓和以色列，都不支持條約。<br />\n<br />\n高美斯說，自美軍1945年在日本廣島和長崎投下原子彈結束二次大戰後，「全球等待這條法律條約已足足有70年&hellip;條約也是超過20年來首條裁減核軍備多邊協議」。<br />\n<br />\n條約將於9月簽署，當有50個國家正式批准，條約便告生效。條約規定所有締約國「在任何情況下永不發展、試驗、製造、生產、取得或儲存核武或其他核爆裝置」，亦禁止轉運、使用或威脅使用核武或其他核爆裝置。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"668f75413b18132290c050c8c98d8af5c1e0768a","tid":314792,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"核武是非法的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議聯合國依法嚴懲核武擁有國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2004270cd45cfb58333d4aebcd8ff03b1b7ea566","tid":314792,"uid":22440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>核武是非法的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議聯合國依法嚴懲核武擁有國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry 打漏左個s <br />\n核武擁有國s"},{"pid":"1d3eb9e79f09d3d70812713e9b0c5f1afdb634cc","tid":314792,"uid":960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"目前已知或相信擁有核武的9個國家，包括美國、俄羅斯、英國、中國、法國、印度、巴基斯坦、<span style=\"color: red;\">北韓</span>和以色列，都不支持條約。<br />\n<br />\n模型玩具來咋吓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad7325c0924ffbb8e8ebc64836af6c48d5e96fb","tid":314792,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>目前已知或相信擁有核武的9個國家，包括美國、俄羅斯、英國、中國、法國、印度、巴基斯坦、<span style=\"color: red;\">北韓</span>和以色列，都不支持條約。<br />\n<br />\n模型玩具來咋吓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9，北韓有飛彈有核電廠，要做核武有幾難？"},{"pid":"7c0180ab32f22b9597191d5bb964564c0448a48e","tid":314792,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>核武是非法的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議聯合國依法嚴懲核武擁有國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加埋都唔夠個9個國家打"},{"pid":"779229517255b5cd0858145b7b14c97401c56772","tid":314792,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"WW3 is 核戰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d6b10d5c2738eb1537034f56affc6fbd7e3337","tid":314792,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"依個post有種同流氓講法律嘅純真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da6d8ca0e4e06b13280db0cd2f754ce960d06b2","tid":314792,"uid":26451,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a34b932fc8b0b6ece47dbc262ac82d9bd77ceb3c","tid":314792,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"此